OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start but rain clearing
OL,6,Feast in the morning, followed by
OL,7,Ffrequent showers interspersed with
OL,8,Fbrief bright intervals. Some of the
OL,9,Fshowers heavy, and turning thundery
OL,10,Finto the afternoon, with a risk of
OL,11,Fhail. Breezy but feeling milder.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers only slowly easing
OL,14,Fovernight, however most areas should
OL,15,Fbecome largely dry by dawn. A brisk
OL,16,Fbreeze continuing overnight, with
OL,17,Ftemperatures on the mild side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
