OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FVariable cloud with
OL,6,Fscattered showers and some bright
OL,7,Fspells, Patchy rain may affect the
OL,8,FPeak District at times. A brisk breeze
OL,9,Fbut feeling warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FThursday, patchy rain easing north
OL,13,Fthen dry and warmer. Friday, very warm
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Chance of thundery
OL,15,Fevening showers. Saturday, very warm
OL,16,Fwith bright spells, thundery showers
OL,17,Fstill possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
